    <title>Linear System</title>
    <url>/2023/08/23/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="Chapter-1-Introduction"><a href="#Chapter-1-Introduction" class="headerlink" title="Chapter 1 Introduction"></a>Chapter 1 Introduction</h2><h3 id="Review-of-Classical-Control-Systems"><a href="#Review-of-Classical-Control-Systems" class="headerlink" title="Review of Classical Control Systems"></a>Review of Classical Control Systems</h3><h4 id="Laplace-Transformation"><a href="#Laplace-Transformation" class="headerlink" title="Laplace Transformation"></a>Laplace Transformation</h4><script type="math/tex; mode=display">
F(s)= \cal{L}[f(t)]=\int_{0}^{\infty}f(t)e^{-st}dt</script><p>Properties of Laplace Transform:</p>
<ol>
<li>$\cal{L}[Af(t)]=A\cal{L} [f(t)]$ where $A$ is a constant.</li>
<li>$\cal{L} [A_1 f_1(t)+A_2 f_2(t)]=A_1 \cal{L} [f_1(t)]+A_2\cal{L} [f_2(t)]$</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="Transfer-Function"><a href="#Transfer-Function" class="headerlink" title="Transfer Function"></a>Transfer Function</h4><p>The transfer function of a linear, time-invariant, differential equation (线性时不变差分方程) is defined as </p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
G(s)=\frac{b_0 s^m+b_1 s^{m-1}+\cdots b_{m-1}s+b_m}{a_0s^n+a_1s^{n-1}+\cdots a_n}</script><p>计算传递函数时，认为初始状态为0.</p>
<h4 id="Other-Definitions"><a href="#Other-Definitions" class="headerlink" title="Other Definitions"></a>Other Definitions</h4><ol>
<li>Proper Transfer Function: $n/geq m$，即传递函数分子的阶数不大于分母的阶数。</li>
<li>Strictly proper transfer function: $n&gt;m$，即传递函数分子阶数小于分母阶数。</li>
<li><em><em>denominator</em></em><em><em>denominator</em></em><em><em>denominator</em></em><em><em>denominator</em></em>or** of G(s).</li>
<li>Poles of G(s): The roots of the denominator polynomial of G(s).</li>
<li>Zeros of G(s): The roots of the numerator polynomial of G(s).</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="Mathematical-Description-of-Systems"><a href="#Mathematical-Description-of-Systems" class="headerlink" title="Mathematical Description of Systems"></a>Mathematical Description of Systems</h3><h4 id="Causality-因果性"><a href="#Causality-因果性" class="headerlink" title="Causality 因果性"></a>Causality 因果性</h4><p>memoryless system:  输出仅取决于当前时刻输入，而不取决于之前的输入和之后的输入。<br>casual system, non-anticipatory system:  系统输出仅取决于之前和当前的输入。</p>
<h4 id="Linear-system"><a href="#Linear-system" class="headerlink" title="Linear system"></a>Linear system</h4><p>通过叠加法则，可将系统响应分解为零状态响应和零输入响应之和，即</p>
<p>零输入响应表示为：</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
\{x(t_0),0,y_{zi}(t)~~for~~ t\geq t_0 \}</script><p>零状态响应表示为：</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
\{0,u(t),~~for~~t\geq t_0, y_{zs}(t)~~for~~ t\geq t_0 \}</script><p>故</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
y(t)=y_{zi}(t)+y_{zs}(t)</script><h3 id="Input-Output-Description"><a href="#Input-Output-Description" class="headerlink" title="Input-Output Description"></a>Input-Output Description</h3><script type="math/tex; mode=display">
y(t)=\int_{t_0}^{t} g(t-\tau)u(\tau)d\tau = u(t)\ast g(t)  \tag{1}</script><p>卷积的连续表达形式。其中 $g(t)$ 是系统对于冲激函数 $\delta(t)$ 的冲激响应 (Impulse Response).</p>
<h3 id="State-Space-Representation"><a href="#State-Space-Representation" class="headerlink" title="State Space Representation"></a>State Space Representation</h3><p>状态空间方程的一般形式</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
\dot{x}(t)=A(t)x(t)+B(t)u(t) \tag{2} \\
y(t)=C(t)x(t)+D(t)u(t)</script><p>其中，$x$ 是 $n$ 维状态矢量； $u$ 是 $p$ 维输入(或控制)矢量； $y$ 是 $q$ 维输出矢量；$A(t)$ 是 $n\times n$ 方阵，为系统内部状态的联系，称为状态矩阵或者系统矩阵；$B(t)$ 是 $n\times p $ 矩阵， 为输入对状态的作用，称为输入矩阵或控制矩阵；$C(t)$ 是 $q\times n$ 矩阵，为输出与状态之间的关系，称为输出矩阵； $D(t)$ 是 $q\times p$ 矩阵，表示系统的输入直接作用在输出的部分，称为直接传递矩阵。</p>
<p>当 $A(t), B(t), C(t), D(t)$ 均为常数时，上述状态空间方程退化为线性时不变方程</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
\dot{x}(t)=Ax(t)+Bu(t) \\
y(t)=Cx(t)+Du(t)  \tag{3}</script><h3 id="Linearization"><a href="#Linearization" class="headerlink" title="Linearization"></a>Linearization</h3><p>暂时还没看懂哈</p>
<h2 id="Chapter-3-State-Space-Solutions-and-Properties"><a href="#Chapter-3-State-Space-Solutions-and-Properties" class="headerlink" title="Chapter 3 State-Space Solutions and Properties"></a>Chapter 3 State-Space Solutions and Properties</h2><p>问题描述：对于(3)中的线性时不变系统，目的是 obtain responses $x(t), y(t)$ for $t\geq t_0$ to initial state $x(t_0)$ and $u(t), t\geq t_0$</p>
<h3 id="Homogeneous-Solution"><a href="#Homogeneous-Solution" class="headerlink" title="Homogeneous Solution"></a>Homogeneous Solution</h3><p>To be continued…</p>
]]></content>
